{"id": 581, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪种开场白最糟糕？", "description": "“小姐你是哪里人啊？”", "record_count": 5433, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145052Q1D9fV6jFa54wkBN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-16T10:54:25Z", "options": [{"id": 21250, "content": "在等人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276065}, {"id": 17667, "content": "最近雾霾真严重啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255026}, {"id": 18691, "content": "..........", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260292}, {"id": 17668, "content": "他好像一条狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253553}, {"id": 17925, "content": "xx！诶不好意思小姐认错人了不去认识一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255842}, {"id": 19973, "content": "你哪里人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266062}, {"id": 19206, "content": "我知道这里的wifi密码哟！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263408}, {"id": 18185, "content": "你化妆了？", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211300FrhmRY64UuxsGWDS.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188948}, {"id": 17930, "content": "听说过安利么朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256250}, {"id": 18186, "content": "你喜欢Sm吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211253voBiFqgth17Y8OHA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241168}, {"id": 17676, "content": "网上的话最讨厌一句话：干嘛呢？  我就不明白了我干嘛关你屁事，碰到这样的绝对不理！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255053}, {"id": 17932, "content": "嗨，吃过饭了吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244529}, {"id": 17679, "content": "多大了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255063}, {"id": 17936, "content": "你看起来好面熟啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212968}, {"id": 17937, "content": "大哥玩不？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218155}, {"id": 17683, "content": "小姐，来给你看个宝贝", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251049}, {"id": 17939, "content": "我来找你玩儿啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225391}, {"id": 17684, "content": "小姐，你的胸掉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251049}, {"id": 17940, "content": "你觉得我怎么样！？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225391}, {"id": 21269, "content": "喂！你好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269004}, {"id": 17691, "content": "美女能加下微信吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222564}, {"id": 17948, "content": "hi，。。。。对不起认错人了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237236}, {"id": 17694, "content": "我有Wi-Fi和充电宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232760}, {"id": 17698, "content": "你好，你是哪里人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252845}, {"id": 19750, "content": "商铺有兴趣吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266530}, {"id": 18728, "content": "干杯?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135849}, {"id": 17705, "content": "女士，看到你的瞬间美的让我无法呼吸！我为了活下来，来问问你有什么好的办法吗？就这样一面？我恐怕不天天见到你，我哪天会窒息！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66235}, {"id": 17707, "content": "美女，你好呀~", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 12806}, {"id": 17964, "content": "玩游戏的时候：hi 你是妹子吗............", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216069}, {"id": 17967, "content": "美女，你是90后吧，这让我觉得很糟糕，说实际年龄吧，很尴尬，不说实际年龄吧，又好像我多装嫩似的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229086}, {"id": 20528, "content": "因为学校查校服。所以每天都会有人问：同学，校裤呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271263}, {"id": 24369, "content": "吃了吗，我擦，什么年代了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278536}, {"id": 17970, "content": "喂！你在哪里？", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211319LsOQy0wWHegTublD.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201373}, {"id": 21300, "content": "拿出绿箭，交个朋友吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276417}, {"id": 17717, "content": "你长的像我前女友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219975}, {"id": 17973, "content": "哎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174155}, {"id": 23093, "content": "你是台灣人嗎", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290446}, {"id": 17718, "content": "你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241619}, {"id": 17975, "content": "不好意思，我不是故意的（却是有心的）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256640}, {"id": 17976, "content": "说话不尊重对方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235594}, {"id": 26424, "content": "你长得特别像我前女友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313720}, {"id": 17721, "content": "喔，小姐你踩我脚了", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211306EOxkB8yNTX4i2Kep.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252723}, {"id": 18745, "content": "小姐，一个人来上厕所啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122608}, {"id": 18236, "content": "你是sb吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193403}, {"id": 17982, "content": "小姐，你吃饭了没", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175772}, {"id": 17987, "content": "吃饭没", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256792}, {"id": 17732, "content": "尊敬的老师们同学们，大家早上好。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255304}, {"id": 17988, "content": "你好漂亮（微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256797}, {"id": 18247, "content": "美女你在这附近工作吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234209}, {"id": 17481, "content": "小姐一个人吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 747, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}]}